description: Gets the Shared Access Authorization Token for the User.

resource_group_name.description: The name of the resource group.

service_name.description: The name of the API Management service.

uid.description: User identifier. Must be unique in the current API Management service instance.

api_version.description: Version of the API to be used with the client request.

subscription_id.description: Subscription credentials which uniquely identify Microsoft Azure subscription. The subscription ID forms part of the URI for every service call.

expiry.description: The Expiry time of the Token. Maximum token expiry time is set to 30 days. The date conforms to the following format: `yyyy-MM-ddTHH:mm:ssZ` as specified by the ISO 8601 standard.

keytype.description: The Key to be used to generate token for user.
